{"tid":392263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU確定22日發表新專輯 感性封面照正式公開","createTime":"2017-09-08T11:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T02:50:06.000Z","uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62bcd5dc6bd68bb3832ff1557aa7f9b4b9a87bb5","tid":392263,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5fe673740e1c61d80fb7caa6c00bac4a/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-09-08/97899-538508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5fe673740e1c61d80fb7caa6c00bac4a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-09-08%2F97899-538508.jpg&h=db175bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU通過經紀公司宣佈，將在9月22日發行第二張翻唱專輯《花書簽2》，新專輯的封面照也公開了！<br />\n<br />\nIU在2014年發行了第一張翻唱專輯《花書簽》，用自己獨特的感性重新詮釋了很多經典歌曲。 這次的新專輯算是續作，也讓人很期待呢！<br />\n<br />\n新專輯的封面照裡，IU穿著白色針織衫、戴著一頂很復古的站長帽，站在一扇玻璃門背後照片被處理成略微褪色的感覺，加上左側的文字，一整個很有舊日情懷~<br />\n<br />\n再看一下第一張翻唱專輯《花書籤》的封面，一眼就能看出是同一系列呢：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_996750e34f997b04f8fd857237b47310/static.koreastardaily.com/2017-09-08/97899-538536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_996750e34f997b04f8fd857237b47310%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2017-09-08%2F97899-538536.jpg&h=b9363e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所屬社表示：「這張專輯選取了多個年齡層都很喜歡的舊日名曲，用IU純粹的音色進行全新詮釋，會給各個年齡層的聽眾帶來共鳴和感動。 」<br />\n<br />\n今年4月IU剛剛發行第四張正規專輯《Palatte》，時隔5個月就發行新專輯，真的勤奮呢！ 希望這次也大發！"},{"pid":"e206ccbe3825f1da5c7ce621f51c433bfb03175c","tid":392263,"uid":70988,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:55:57.000Z","msg":"睇左性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a01709368bc8b844b12dbcc017cd78a723613c3","tid":392263,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T11:59:03.000Z","msg":"上次隻 &lt;你的意義&gt; 好好聽"},{"pid":"33302fbe9f301b84c762c39a8a0c8014aa3697d8","tid":392263,"uid":9276